{"tid":1377740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"\"亞洲紅點傳媒”好恐怖","createTime":"2019-07-28T14:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T06:16:27.000Z","uid":289857,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"990e3ade31433bf11adb71c6575c08e014e5b500","tid":1377740,"uid":289857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:29:34.000Z","msg":"我係第一次開po嘅P牌仔 <br />\n唔太熟悉點運作 操作錯左嘅求放過<br />\n<br />\n頭先教老豆老母點subscribe  youtube channel (佢地唔識用)<br />\n發現主頁推薦個堆channel有一個叫&quot;亞洲紅點傳媒&quot;嘅channel<br />\n望左陣  目測youtube主係馬來西亞人(?要再check真啲不過唔係重點<br />\n最近啲內容全部係抹黑反送中運動<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不停誤導他人 話香港人（示威者）暴動</span></span></span><br />\n用左啲Fact checked左就會發現有問題嘅資訊<br />\n下面啲五毛留言好多話要殺哂香港暴徒/出老解/廢青<br />\n大家快啲check下老豆老母有冇睇依個channel<br />\n條友扮中立 睇標題就知佢偏頗到cls<br />\n唔好比班中年人接收錯誤資訊<br />\n佢地真係會信㗎<br />\n好彩老豆老母聽到啲咩會同我fact check<br />\n如果唔係 一傳十 十傳百 好易誤傳<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d19db4e7cdf694ca149183d7745e3ae983daf22","tid":1377740,"uid":1627,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:41:21.000Z","msg":"推，仲有個小馬識途<br />\n呢兩條撚屌都係馬來西亞人，表面同你講我係中立，實際撐中撐到出曬面"},{"pid":"e4f52ba5d9b4d6090533aac96ebee5488f7549c2","tid":1377740,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d19db4e7cdf694ca149183d7745e3ae983daf22","tid":1377740,"uid":1627,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:41:21.000Z","msg":"推，仲有個小馬識途<br />\n呢兩條撚屌都係馬來西亞人，表面同你講我係中立，實際撐中撐到出曬面"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:44:50.000Z","msg":"有個乜撚大叔channel，又係馬拉佬"},{"pid":"46e1c8331b0a8100828a936d4357fd814455093f","tid":1377740,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:47:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2e1z67e9Dto\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihk